    "description": "<strong>Make up a person by combining body parts!</strong><br><br>&quot;Make Up Human&quot; is a 3D puzzle game.<br>Drop human body parts such as eyes and ears into a box.<br><br>When the same parts come into contact with each other, they will change into the next level part.<br><br>Parts will age over time and will never be able to change again.<br>Be careful, as in rare cases they may not age and become cancerous!<br><br>If you're lucky, you might find a special part that can change any part.<br><br>If even one part falls outside the box, it's game over.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Video Distribution</h2>・Distribution is available without permission.<br>・Monetization is only possible when using the functions provided by the video distribution site.<br>・We would appreciate it if you include the name of the game in the title of your video or live broadcast, or include a link to the Steam page in the summary section.<br><br>We will not be liable for any damages caused by the distribution of videos of this game.<br>The contents of these guidelines are subject to change without notice.",
